{"tid":1833813,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟當初沙士源頭黃杏初(初仔)係點樣成為第一個感染者？","createTime":"2020-01-22T05:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T10:45:34.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f8c6ba18f34831825f49b0ef3f79d732d64966","tid":1833813,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"對於有傳言說黃杏初染病與他的工作要宰殺野生動物有關，新華社報道引述黃杏初的話說，他的工作是廚師，接觸的是鍋碗，宰殺雞鴨等都是小廚工做的事情，他並沒有做這些工作，而做這些工作的同事並沒有染上SARS病毒。"},{"pid":"a2047cff7df2fb13a0d8ecd622b9cd56ab85837f","tid":1833813,"uid":184370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年有沙士會唔會係控制我地既其中一步"},{"pid":"1e06a90b685882535c0889a75e3e752ae611d055","tid":1833813,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ada3343f1d865bda0a2f62b8447017e93a72de","tid":1833813,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2047cff7df2fb13a0d8ecd622b9cd56ab85837f","tid":1833813,"uid":184370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年有沙士會唔會係控制我地既其中一步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"初仔康復之後不停接受官媒訪問話冇接觸動物好撚可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b576e80f55836ebaf038515280eccf09b122df0","tid":1833813,"uid":55321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"屌左果子狸？"},{"pid":"6ff5a7e51556617d1460ccd936731419eecc36d0","tid":1833813,"uid":261332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08ada3343f1d865bda0a2f62b8447017e93a72de","tid":1833813,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2047cff7df2fb13a0d8ecd622b9cd56ab85837f","tid":1833813,"uid":184370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年有沙士會唔會係控制我地既其中一步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"初仔康復之後不停接受官媒訪問話冇接觸動物好撚可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"都咪話唔邪<br />\n02 年提出23 條，結果02年尾就沙士。<br />\n而家..."},{"pid":"aa8e2dd674655762b075dda6e8480612706f3458","tid":1833813,"uid":288511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:56:01.000Z","msg":"02年展開廿三條立法 -&gt; 反廿三條 -&gt; 03年沙士<br />\n19年展開送中立法 -&gt; 反送中 -&gt; 20年武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"0ccd80913d76470a48c075ecbd2b6cd9b51e4a57","tid":1833813,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"蔡同榮批評，黃杏初根本就是中國刻意誤導疫情的樣板，真正流行「中國肺炎」的時間，根本不是黃杏初感染發病的去年十一月，而是在更早之前。台灣握有在去年一月因肺部病變在東莞去世的黃璉華弟弟的X光片，經由台大醫院感染科主任張上淳確認後，證實就是SARS 死亡病例，而台灣這一張來自大陸的X光片，就是證明中國大陸早已流傳SARS病毒致死的鐵證，時間應該在前年年底前。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡同榮強調，中國為隱瞞疫情，刻意將職業是負責宰殺野味的廚師黃杏初列為首位通報SARS案例，當時中共官方在廣州開會時，就認定因大部份感染「非典」的病人，很多都是從事野生動物有關的工作，將SARS病毒染病來源推給與野生動物有關。"},{"pid":"676cef16b2cc828f298b932842868c85787e3c5f","tid":1833813,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79e8645aa9734726cd4a22562483ff6071f9f74b","tid":1833813,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbb6029f3bbc3e14b8f0c9be95147d5e6c1495fb","tid":1833813,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b576e80f55836ebaf038515280eccf09b122df0","tid":1833813,"uid":55321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"屌左果子狸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img